<h2 align="center"><u>Bechelor In Education</u> </h2>
<p align="justify" class="pagefont">The           Department of B.Ed. was established in 2002 in the B.V.M. College . It is&nbsp;presently running           BEd / DEd Curriculum          for the College. It comprises of highly qualified and&nbsp;hard-working faculties.</p>
<p align="justify" class="pagefont">The Secondary Teacher Education programme, commonly           known as B.Ed., is meant for preparing teachers for senior secondary schools.           B.Ed. programme is approved by NCTE, New Delhi and affiliated to Jiwaji           University, Gwalior.          B.Ed. trained teachers are eligible as T.G.T. for Central School, Navodaya           Vidhyalaya, Delhi Municipal Co-orporation Schools, Madhyamic Siksha Chayan           Board, Specific B.T.C. Uttar Pradesh Samvida-Sikshak, various exams of           P.S.C. and other competitive exams. After doing B.Ed. one can seek admission           in M.Ed.</p>
<p align="justify" class="pagefont"> The BEd / DEd course is approved by NCTE ,New Delhi and         Department of higher education, Bhopal, Govt of&nbsp; M.P. and is affiliated to         Jiwaji Univ. Gwl.</p>
<ul><li><p align="justify" class="pagefont"><strong>Recognition Code</strong>:  APW02407/222059</p>
