<p align="justify" class="pagefont">B.Ed. The admission will be given through a centralized         counseling&nbsp;of passing candidates of PRE-B.Ed. Entrance examination conducted         by VYPAM,&nbsp;M.P.&nbsp;</p>
<p align="justify" class="pagefont">Minimum Pass Marks in Internal Exams is 60% in individual courses. External          xamination is Conducted by R.G.P.Vishwavidyalaya,Bhopal with each Theory Paper          of 100 Marks.&nbsp;Minimum pass marks in Theory Paper is 40%. Practical Exams is          conducted for programming&nbsp;lab of 100 Marks &amp; Practical paper is of 50 Marks.          Minimum pass marks in Practical Exams&nbsp;are 50% with both papers.</p>
